results.reasoning: CPT code 41105 is for excision of lesion of tongue without closure, which is the most appropriate code for excision of an oral lesion on the floor of the mouth. Since this is an excision (not biopsy) of a lesion in the oral cavity (floor of mouth), 41105 is the correct choice.
